<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我<delay8 />有一个惊喜<delay20 />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要送给<tag a="110" b="4" />喔！<delay frames="40" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当当！<delay20 />就是这个，收下吧！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那个，<delay20 />这个请求或许有些突然……<delay20 />
能不能请你收下<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />？</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你最近<delay20 />
