<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我总感觉之前好像<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听别人有这么说过<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我没有找呀</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">怎么回事？</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎～<delay8 />就知道！<delay20 />我这人总是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一不小心就忘记家里已经有
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />2个<delay20 /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多出的这个放着也不用，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />你不介意的话，<delay20 />
