	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这就是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你不喜欢的话，<delay8 />
丢掉它也没关系哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然现在到了<tag a="110" b="4" />手里，<delay8 />
就希望你能够善待它吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实是我之前买回这个之后，<delay20 />
有个朋友又送了我一件<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />完全一模一样的东西啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我实在是用不上，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是也一直很珍视它，<delay20 />
始终舍不得把它丢掉～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<tag a="110" b="4" />愿意
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拿去用的话，<delay8 />我会很开心的～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你不用的话，<delay20 />
