<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总之你愿意接手<delay8 />就帮了我大忙啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="300" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦，<delay8 />是这样吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底当初是谁说的来着～<delay40 />
