<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实当初找到它的时候就已经为你预留好了，<delay20 />
不介意的话就免费送给你啦！</message>
	<message label="301" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay8 />是我搞错了吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，无所谓啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟平时都一直受<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
照顾了那么久对吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以之前一眼扫到这个<delay20 />
