我就果断买下来了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就当作是我送给你的礼物吧，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你愿意接受，我会很开心的～</message>
	<message label="302" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你觉得用不上的话，<delay20 />
