<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也不介意的哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="303" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喜欢的话就用上吧！<delay40 />
